Sure, here are five example sentences in Serbian that use the word "rep" in different forms and positions:

1. Moj pas ima dugačak *rep*. (My dog has a long tail.)
2. Da li biste mi dali malo više *repa*? (Could you give me a bit more of the turnip?)
3. Nakon duge vožnje, imao sam *bol u donjem delu leđa* koji se protezao sve do *repa*. (After a long drive, I had lower back pain that extended all the way down to my tailbone.)
4. Pre nekoliko godina sam krenula u teretanu da bih učvrstila *trbušne mišiće i rep*. (A few years ago, I started going to the gym to strengthen my abdominal muscles and glutes.)
5. U žurbi sam ostavila svoj *repka* kod kuće. (I left my backpack at home in a hurry.)

I hope this helps!